Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:15.95,Dialogue mini,,0,0,0,,P-Prosím. ne—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:18.08,Dialogue mini,,0,0,0,,Ne, jsou to {\i1}moje{\i0} brýle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.13,Dialogue mini,,0,0,0,,Brýle!
